    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>官方QQ群：</strong>653050279 有问题可以留言给小助理~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>存档提示</strong>：游戏可自动存档、手动存档，其中自动存档会在游戏每月初结算后进行，与实际游玩进度相较有一定延迟，建议多进行手动存档。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为新晋丰收之神，您将探索美食与冒险的世界。收集各种食材，如海鲜、香料和水果，通过航海发现遥远岛屿。与当地居民贸易，传播美食，提升饮食品质。管理资源，发展种植和贸易网络，创造繁荣和美食王国。加入这个美食冒险旅程，享受食材的奇遇和美味的探索！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/5fb227ee5e9b0c1ef448f51bc47b3af5.poster.avif?t=1737106804\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/5fb227ee5e9b0c1ef448f51bc47b3af5.webm?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/5fb227ee5e9b0c1ef448f51bc47b3af5.mp4?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>※ 真实的世界地图！※</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >环游世界，体验各地别样的风土人情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/cd298cee16c5143881db72b41fd0e11c.poster.avif?t=1737106804\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/cd298cee16c5143881db72b41fd0e11c.webm?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/cd298cee16c5143881db72b41fd0e11c.mp4?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>※ 特色的各地饮食！※</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义每个城市的饮食文化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/78206f9ac7d132a57f790cc3042138a3.poster.avif?t=1737106804\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/78206f9ac7d132a57f790cc3042138a3.webm?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/78206f9ac7d132a57f790cc3042138a3.mp4?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>※ 丰富的原产食材！※</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >查阅大量史料，还原真实食材历史！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/d464705b2300c4f457d80e740edee0b5.poster.avif?t=1737106804\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/d464705b2300c4f457d80e740edee0b5.webm?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※ <strong>独特的丰收之神体验！</strong>※</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有神力的丰收之神又该如何传播美食？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/f7aec2cba3cde640be706e23014db9c4.poster.avif?t=1737106804\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/f7aec2cba3cde640be706e23014db9c4.webm?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/f7aec2cba3cde640be706e23014db9c4.mp4?t=1737106804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※ <strong>直观的健康提升体验！</strong>※</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界各地的人们将在你的努力下愈发健康强壮！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/5ced2657969a817028bb759ce7d2b85a.webp?t=1737106804\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264820/extras/5ced2657969a817028bb759ce7d2b85a.poster.avif?t=1737106804\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=337 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立即加入我们，成为丰收之神，开启一段充满挑战与美味的冒险之旅！通过您的智慧与努力，将全球的美食与健康传播到每个角落！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
